snippet.title: cancellation culture wants to remove Amber Heard and Ezra Millar
snippet.description:
The dc universe a passion that took me on a mission ever since seeing man of steel to protect that movie and everthing since.though out all the media i created platforms where like minded people can share their positive views about the dceu that zack created and finally we got our wish and we were given Zacks justice league.
I thought we had done it ive got nothing more to give so as i shut down my many platforms i found i couldnt shut this one down for this old DC fan will always be driven to go beyond what i originally intended to achieve and i find alot of comfort sharing my thoughts with you. so please subscribe an tell me your thoughts.

https://boundingintocomics.com/2020/08/15/new-rumor-provides-update-on-amber-heard-and-ezra-millers-status-at-warner-bros/
